{"tid":760560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老婦伊院照大腸　導管錯插陰道須切輸卵管","createTime":"2018-07-29T15:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T03:47:51.000Z","uid":71071,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"14810e44415a17d32ad5600a169441e79b78b277","tid":760560,"uid":71071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T15:38:19.000Z","msg":"無嘢呀，咁都插錯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n伊利沙伯醫院發生醫療事故，一名79歲老婦進行大腸造影檢查，有5年經驗的放射師將導管經肛門置入腸道時，疑不當置入陰道，致造影劑殘留在病人的陰道、子宮及輸卵管，或引致腹腔炎，病人須切除輸卵管。有腸胃科醫生指，有關事故可以致命。病人組織直斥事件難以理解及不能接受，指家屬要求解釋及賠償。伊院則向病人及其家屬致歉。"},{"pid":"db5add92a3ddfa3eafcb83102edb7534a8edf9d6","tid":760560,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5c98b5bc9f14755b6d55d032dea59bc9c26533f","tid":760560,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T15:40:26.000Z","msg":"<ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">@happyplaza</span></ins>"},{"pid":"343c9706adb6fe252b6b10de0f107a10f80bf278","tid":760560,"uid":71071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db5add92a3ddfa3eafcb83102edb7534a8edf9d6","tid":760560,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T15:41:12.000Z","msg":"事件中涉及2名5年及20年年資的放射科技師，分別負責置入導管及在旁監察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通係青頭仔？"},{"pid":"823b4906ba75efe5af5e916ce45045d8c07e02d3","tid":760560,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T15:43:13.000Z","msg":"阿婆下面變到肉醬咁好難分？"},{"pid":"3a76cc3b7658f008c7f852094b5820c381f226bc","tid":760560,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T15:47:22.000Z","msg":"唔敢睇合埋眼插？"},{"pid":"238bf9d06046379ed2cfd87040fc0be87e7ad0bd","tid":760560,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T15:49:40.000Z","msg":"個呀婆後生玩到咩程度先會分唔到西既